OL,10,FA chef who robbed seven shops across
OL,11,FStaffordshire and threatened staff at
OL,12,Fknifepoint has been jailed.
OL,14,FPatryk Slepowronski, 22, of Marston
OL,15,FMontgomery, Derbyshire, carried out a
OL,16,Fstring of offences in Upper Tean,
OL,17,FUttoxeter, Hixon, Stafford and
OL,18,FBentilee between November 2024 and
OL,19,FJanuary 2025.
