OL,6,FStaffordshire Police arrested
OL,7,FSlepowronski after a DNA hit came back
OL,8,Ffrom a knifepoint robbery in Hixon on
OL,9,F24 December 2024.
OL,11,FSafe keys and money that had been
OL,12,Ftaken from a number of the robberies
OL,13,Fwere found at his home.
OL,15,FSlepowronski pleaded guilty to six
OL,16,Fcounts of robbery and one count of
OL,17,Fattempted robbery, and has been jailed
OL,18,Ffor 12 years.
