OL,6,FHe also pleaded guilty to eight counts
OL,7,Fof robbery, seven counts of possession
OL,8,Fof a bladed article in a public place
OL,9,Fand one count of attempted robbery for
OL,10,Fsimilar offences in Derbyshire,
OL,11,Fbetween July and December 2024.
OL,13,F"Prolific in his offending"
OL,15,FPC Libby May Houston, who investigated
OL,16,Fthe case, said: "Slepowronksi was
OL,17,Fprolific in his offending and caused
OL,18,Fsignificant distress and alarm to
OL,19,Fthose who were unfortunate enough to
OL,20,Fbe faced with him in these robberies.
